    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained chickpeas</strong> to a<strong> food processor </strong>with your<strong> tahini </strong>and <strong>half</strong> of the<strong> chopped garlic</strong> (save the rest for later!)</p><p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong>, 50ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [75ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>and a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Blitz until smooth – this is your<strong> hummus</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a small splash more water if your hummus is looking a little thick!</p>",
