      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>lamb mince</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until browned, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
